/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00de1624012202e8fad7120feaa239939ae1371","tid":636622,"uid":45518,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:29:27.000Z","msg":"痴撚線, 係咁贏, 邊夠你玩呀"},{"pid":"5bd646f00beafa785462f4c70f3ba4a451695367","tid":636622,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3448f4c41a6452849a8fd59bd7d1ffbcc5711fe3","tid":636622,"uid":123711,"like":135,"dislike":3,"score":132,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:18:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:30:13.000Z","msg":"點都贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e442c05d2cbae7784728243ff6d23d7b0d3321","tid":636622,"uid":43042,"like":102,"dislike":1,"score":101,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/132951_4d02a526a8b2d340f41816e122c5be5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F132951_4d02a526a8b2d340f41816e122c5be5b.jpg&h=a31c6cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重有砸腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad8e4231c940c3dfba946074225a568006e0340","tid":636622,"uid":77556,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:39:47.000Z","msg":"連登討論中國 中國或成為最大贏家"},{"pid":"66b87779f8413f8fea134fcec83a796bf2cc4c42","tid":636622,"uid":125809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:40:21.000Z","msg":"輸得太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ce09155026de5b29722f5b55d3d42132fbd000","tid":636622,"uid":12404,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:45:46.000Z","msg":"CCTVB: 消息人士指X國旨在圍堵中國，中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774a262dd46e8508f9c061ee5dd530059c951b64","tid":636622,"uid":2054,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"43ce09155026de5b29722f5b55d3d